---
title: Ultra-Creamy Risotto with Mushrooms and Artichokes
description: You could think of risotto as a blank canvas that can be embellished with whatever ingredients you please. Here, we’re dressing it up with tender roasted artichoke hearts, earthy mushrooms, and some pine nuts for crunch. Altogether, it makes for a masterful composition that’s a delight to take in.
